I bear witness that none has the right to be worshipped but Allah alone,
Who has no partner;
and I bear witness that Muhammad is His slave and His Messenger

I seek refuge in the Perfect Words of Allah
from His anger and His punishment,
from the evil of His slaves,
and from the taunts of devils and from their presence.

U`īthukumā bikalimāti ‘llāhit-tāmmati min kulli shayṭānin wa hāmmah, wa min kulli `aynin lāmmah I seek protection for you in the Perfect Words of Allah
from every devil and every beast,
and from every envious blameworthy eye.
